Walaupun anda berhenti

00:25:53.880 --> 00:25:55.530
Tali Cukur Boneka yang paling tajam,

00:25:56.110 --> 00:25:56.940
satu-satunya senjata tanpa pisau

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.250
di dunia,

00:25:58.680 --> 00:25:59.530
anda akan dicabik-cabik

00:25:59.590 --> 00:26:01.810
saat anda menyekatnya.

